Homepage: https://worldfoundry.org/develop/blender/
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: worldfoundry-blender
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 blender (>= 4.2),
 python3,
 worldfoundry-engine-build-deps
Recommends: worldfoundry-blender-addon
Description: Blender 4.2+ configured for World Foundry level authoring
 Pulls in Blender 4.2+ (Ubuntu 26.04 ships 5.0.1 in universe — no PPA
 needed; the snap is unsuitable because its sandbox blocks the
 debug-bridge TCP port the WF addon uses) plus the Python and build
 toolchain required to build the wf_core.so native module shipped with
 the wf_blender addon.
 .
 The addon itself is in worldfoundry-blender-addon (Recommends, not
 Depends, so you can build it from source if you prefer).
